1. *Čekao* je dugo da mu odgovore. (He waited a long time for them to answer.)
2. Ona je *čekala* dok on nije završio. (She waited until he finished.)
3. *Čekali* su da se vrata otvore. (They waited for the doors to open.)
4. Oni su *čekali* da vidim šta će da se desi. (They waited to see what would happen.)
5. Ona je *čekala* da čuje njegov odgovor. (She waited to hear his answer.)
6. *Čekali* su da vidi ko će da dođe. (They waited to see who would come.)